text:
EFL In Rood health Wayne Rooney could receive an incredible £15MILLION pay-off from Manchester United if he makes £52m-a-year move to Chinese Super League this summer 
England forward's agent is currently in China negotiating a deal to make him the highest-paid player in world football By Dave Fraser
